00:00:13.520 --> 00:00:15.320 align:middle
Got it, sosu.

00:00:15.320 --> 00:00:18.660 align:middle
That nice-smelling Hollow child has been taken, sosu?

00:00:18.660 --> 00:00:21.120 align:middle
