00:00:38.140 --> 00:00:40.100 align:middle
Reg...

00:00:39.050 --> 00:00:41.640 align:middle
That face swimming around in my memory...

00:00:42.060 --> 00:00:45.650 align:middle
It must have something to do with this promise.

00:00:45.650 --> 00:00:50.880 align:middle
Faputa, can you tell me what the promise is just one more time?

00:00:51.360 --> 00:00:53.650 align:middle
If it's something only I can do, 
I'd like to see it through.

00:00:56.610 --> 00:00:59.530 align:middle
I don't want to force you to make a sacrifice.

00:00:59.530 --> 00:01:00.910 align:middle
But instead,

00:01:00.910 --> 00:01:04.160 align:middle
can you lend us some of your know... ledge?

00:01:04.160 --> 00:01:07.120 align:middle
No need for that, sosu.

00:01:17.220 --> 00:01:19.320 align:middle
Wh-What are you...

00:01:20.600 --> 00:01:25.360 align:middle
All of Faputa is fair trade for the promise, sosu.

00:01:25.360 --> 00:01:30.060 align:middle
Come now, we will eradicate them together, sosu.

00:01:31.440 --> 00:01:34.530 align:middle
I wonder why we ever came to a place like this.

00:01:37.320 --> 00:01:40.580 align:middle
I wonder why things ever ended up like this.

00:01:41.530 --> 00:01:45.500 align:middle
No one can give us answers to those questions.

00:01:47.710 --> 00:01:52.960 align:middle
That is because we are here as a result of choices we ourselves made.

00:01:54.380 --> 00:01:58.340 align:middle
We alone have to find those answers.

00:01:58.710 --> 00:01:59.720 align:middle
It's all good.

00:02:02.100 --> 00:02:04.310 align:middle
I gave everybody else some, too.

00:02:04.310 --> 00:02:05.480 align:middle
No matter

00:02:06.770 --> 00:02:08.610 align:middle
what those answers turn out to be.

