00:21:50.160 --> 00:21:51.450 align:middle
No matter how many times...

00:21:58.370 --> 00:22:04.460 align:middle
Normally, Irumyuui wouldn't have the strength left to even maintain the village

00:22:04.460 --> 00:22:07.680 align:middle
